I had our garage built with 10 foot ceilings and 9 foot doors and my 
highroof bus fits inside with room to spare.  I can jack it up pretty 
high once inside, too.  And another benefit to 10 foot ceilings that I 
never see discussed - it is so much cooler inside in the hot summer months.

